<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idbdf95cd9-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s7176"><num value="7176">§ 7176.</num><heading> Reorganization</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">For the purposes of chapter 9 of title 5 the Commission shall be deemed to be an independent regulatory agency.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idbdf95cda-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">(<ref href="/us/pl/95/91/tIV/s406">Pub. L. 95–91, title IV, § 406</ref>, <date date="1977-08-04">Aug. 4, 1977</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/91/586">91 Stat. 586</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
